data.description: This is a great little community of home owners. Most of us are younger couples with children of daycare, preschool, elementary or junior high school age. We are right behind a church and there are several law enforcement officers that live in the area. It’s one of the safest places I remember living! It is wonderful!
data.whatILove: The house is open so I can see my front door from my back yard! It's beautiful! The view of the mountains is unparallel! And the land behind the back yard should never be built up because it is land owned by the church.
